"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nuovo "
"collegamento simbolico...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creates a symbolic link to the currently selected file."
