"shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deseleziona gruppo...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The opposite of <guimenuitem>Select Group</guimenuitem>. The files that "
"match the pattern in the active panel will be deselected."
msgstr ""
"Il contrario di <guimenuitem>Seleziona gruppo</guimenuitem>. I file che "
"corrispondono al modello, nel pannello attivo, saranno deselezionati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seleziona tutto</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects all files in the active panel. You can also select all folders by "
"activating the <guilabel>Autoselect folders</guilabel> option in the <link "
"linkend=\"konfig-panel\">Konfigurator Panel page</link>."
msgstr ""
"Seleziona tutti i file nel pannello attivo. Puoi anche selezionare tutte le "
"cartelle attivando l'opzione <guilabel>Selezione automatica cartella</"
"guilabel> nella <link linkend=\"konfig-panel\">pagina Pannello di "
"Konfigurator</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unselect All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Deseleziona tutto</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unselects all the files in the active panel."
msgstr "Deseleziona tutti i file nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>*</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Invert Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>*</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Inverti la selezione</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inverts the selection status of all the files in the active panel (&ie; "
"selected files will become unselected and deselected files will become "
"selected)."
msgstr ""
"Inverte lo stato di selezione di tutti i file presenti nel pannello attivo "
"(&ie;, i file selezionati saranno deselezionati e viceversa)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Restore Selection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ripristina la selezione</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restore the selection status of previously unselected items."
msgstr ""
"Ripristina lo stato della selezione degli elementi precedentemente "
"deselezionati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find in folder...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Trova nella cartella...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles &krusader; <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">quick search</link> "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Attiva/disattiva la funzione di <link linkend=\"quicksearch\">ricerca "
"rapida</link> di &krusader;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Confronta "
"cartelle</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles &krusader; <link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Compare Folders</link> "
"function."
msgstr ""
"Attiva/disattiva la funzione <link linkend=\"compare-dir\">Confronta "
"cartelle</link> di &krusader;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:577
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare Setup</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Impostazioni confronto file</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configures the <guimenuitem>Compare Folders</guimenuitem> function."
msgstr ""
"Permette di configurare la funzione <guimenuitem>Confronta cartelle</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Select Newer and Single</guimenuitem> (default)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Seleziona più recenti e singoli</guimenuitem> (opzione "
"predefinita)"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menu-commands.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Single"
msgstr "Seleziona singoli"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menu-commands.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Newer"
msgstr "Seleziona più recenti"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menu-commands.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different and Single"
msgstr "Seleziona diversi e singoli"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: menu-commands.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Different"
msgstr "Seleziona diversi"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:615
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Calculate Occupied Space</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Calcola spazio occupato</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"calculate\">Calculates occupied space</link> of files and "
"folders, archives and remote filesystems."
msgstr ""
"Permette di <link linkend=\"calculate\">calcolare lo spazio occupato</link> "
"di file, cartelle, archivi e file system remoti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keysym>Return</keysym></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keysym>Invio</keysym></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Modifica</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Proprietà...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the properties dialog for the currently selected file. (KP refers to "
"Key Pad.)"
msgstr ""
"Apre la finestra delle proprietà per il file attualmente selezionato (TN si "
"riferisce al tastierino numerico)."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go Menu"
msgstr "Menu Vai"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Su</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:660
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigates to the parent folder of the active panel."
msgstr "Passa alla cartella superiore del pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Indietro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigates to the previously viewed folder in the active panel."
msgstr "Passa alla cartella precedentemente visualizzata nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Right;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Avanti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigates to the next viewed folder in the active panel. Becomes available "
"only if <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> was used beforehand."
msgstr ""
"Passa alla cartella visualizzata successiva nel pannello attivo. Diventa "
"disponibile solo se <menuchoice><guimenu>Vai</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Indietro</guimenuitem></menuchoice> è stato utilizzato in "
"precedenza."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Home;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Home</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; &Home;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Home</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigates to the home folder of the current user."
msgstr "Passa alla cartella home dell'utente attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Backspace;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Root</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Backspace;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Radice</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigates to the root folder of the system."
msgstr "Passa alla cartella radice del sistema."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:731
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Popular &URL;s...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>&URL; ricorrenti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a listing of frequently viewed folders from which you may navigate "
"to one by double-clicking on it."
msgstr ""
"Mostra un elenco delle cartelle più visitate da cui partire, tramite doppio "
"clic, per la loro navigazione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Set Jump Back "
"Point</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Imposta il punto "
"per il salto indietro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the current folder as a <quote>jump back</quote> point. To navigate to "
"this folder quickly, select the <guimenuitem>Jump Back</guimenuitem> command "
"from the <guimenu>Go</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Imposta la cartella attuale come punto per il <quote>salto indietro</quote>. "
"Per navigare rapidamente a questa cartella, seleziona il comando "
"<guimenuitem>Salto indietro</guimenuitem> dal menu <guimenuitem>Vai</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Go</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Jump Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Vai</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Salta indietro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns to a previous <quote>jump back</quote> point."
msgstr ""
"Ritorna a un punto precedente effettuato con un <quote>salto indietro</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:782
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Menu"
msgstr "Menu Visualizza"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The action in this submenu usually affects the current &krusader; session. "
"If you want to make permanent changes use <link linkend=\"konfigurator"
"\">Konfigurator Startup page</link>."
msgstr ""
"Le azioni intraprese in questo menu in genere riguardano la sessione "
"corrente di &krusader;. Se vuoi apportare modifiche permanenti, usa la <link "
"linkend=\"konfigurator\">pagina Avvio di Konfigurator</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom In</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom avanti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase the view scale."
msgstr "Aumenta la scala di visualizzazione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom Out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom indietro</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decrease the view scale."
msgstr "Diminuisce la scala di visualizzazione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Default Zoom</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zoom predefinito</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset the view scale."
msgstr "Azzera la scala di visualizzazione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Alt;&Shift; <keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Detailed View</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Alt;&Shift; <keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vista "
"dettagliata</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows the file names, file size, creation date and time and their attributes."
msgstr ""
"Mostra i nomi dei file, la loro dimensione, la data e l'ora di creazione e i "
"loro attributi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Alt;&Shift; <keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Brief View</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Alt;&Shift; <keycap>B</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vista "
"sintetica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:849
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows only the file names."
msgstr "Mostra solo i nomi dei file."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:854
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Hidden Files</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mostra i file nascosti</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the option to display the hidden files in the &krusader; panels."
msgstr ""
"Attiva/disattiva l'opzione che permette la visualizzazione dei file nascosti "
"nei pannelli di &krusader;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F10</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>All Files</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F10</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Tutti i "
"file</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Turns off all filters and display all files."
msgstr "Disattiva tutti i filtri e mostra tutti i file."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F12</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Custom</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift; <keycap>F12</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Personalizzato</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to install a custom filter on the &krusader; panel. Only files "
"that match the filter pattern(s) and folders will be displayed. Do not "
"forget to deactivate the custom filter after use, or some files may not be "
"visible."
msgstr ""
"Permette di installare un filtro personalizzato da applicare al pannello di "
"&krusader;. Saranno visualizzati solo i file che corrispondono al modello, o "
"modelli, del filtro. Non dimenticare di disattivare questo filtro dopo l'uso "
"altrimenti alcuni file non saranno visibili."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Previews</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mostra le anteprime</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:910
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, show the previews for all files and folders on the active panel."
msgstr ""
"Se selezionata, mostra le anteprime per tutti i file e le cartelle nel "
"pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select Remote Charset</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Seleziona insieme di caratteri "
"remoto</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:921
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects the remote charset for <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Remote "
"Connections</link>."
msgstr ""
"Permette di selezionare l'insieme di caratteri remoto per le <link linkend="
"\"remote-connections\">connessioni remote</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Reload</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ricarica</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Refreshes the contents of the active panel."
msgstr "Aggiorna il contenuto del pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save settings as default</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Salva le impostazioni come "
"predefinite</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:948
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to save the view settings of the current tab for new instances of "
"this view type."
msgstr ""
"Ti permette di salvare le impostazioni di visualizzazione della scheda "
"attiva per le nuove istanze di questo tipo di visualizzazione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply settings to other tabs</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Visualizza</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Applica le impostazioni alle "
"altre schede</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to apply the view settings of the current tab to the other tabs."
msgstr ""
"Ti permette di applicare le impostazioni di visualizzazione della scheda "
"attiva alle altre schede."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Useractions Menu"
msgstr "Menu Azioni"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can add your own menu entries here by defining your own <link linkend="
"\"useractions\">UserActions</link>."
msgstr ""
"Puoi aggiungere le voci personalizzate nel tuo menu qui, definendo le tue "
"<link linkend=\"useractions\">azioni</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Useractions</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Manage User Actions...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Azioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Gestione azioni...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:977
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the <link linkend=\"useractions\">UserActions</link> manager."
msgstr "Apre il gestore delle <link linkend=\"useractions\">azioni</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:983
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>A</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>Multimedia</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Enqueue in Amarok</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>A</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Multimedia</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Accoda in Amarok</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:995
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appends selected item(s) to &amarok; playlist."
msgstr "Aggiunge gli elementi selezionati alla scaletta di &amarok;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt; </keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>Samples</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Equal panel-size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt; </keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Esempi</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pannelli alla stessa dimensione</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the ratio between the two panels to 50/50."
msgstr "Imposta i pannelli alla stessa dimensione."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>Samples</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Edit as root</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Esempi</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Modifica come amministratore</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to edit a file with <application>kwrite</application> using root "
"permissions."
msgstr ""
"Permette di modificare un file in <application>kwrite</application> con "
"permessi di amministratore."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>M</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>Samples</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Mount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>M</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Esempi</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Monta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1045
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mounts a new filesystem."
msgstr "Monta un nuovo file system."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>C</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>Samples</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Copy current item to clipboard</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>C</keycap> </"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Esempi</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Copia elemento corrente negli appunti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copies current item name to the clipboard."
msgstr "Copia il nome dell'elemento corrente negli appunti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1067
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta;<keycap>F5</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Backup current</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta;<keycap>F5</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Crea una copia di "
"sicurezza del file corrente</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Backups current file in current folder and asks the user for a new filename. "
"By default <literal role=\"extension\">.old</literal> is appended to the "
"original filename."
msgstr ""
"Crea una copia di sicurezza del file corrente nell'attuale cartella e chiede "
"all'utente di attribuire un nuovo nome file. Per impostazione predefinita, "
"al file originale viene aggiunta l'estensione <literal role=\"extension\">."
"old</literal>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>1</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>User Interface</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Sort By Name</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>1</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Interfaccia utente</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ordina per nome</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this action is turned on, the main sorting key in the &krusader; panel "
"becomes the file name."
msgstr ""
"Quando questa azione è attivata, la chiave principale di ordinamento, "
"all'interno del pannello di &krusader;, è il nome del file."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>2</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>User Interface</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Sort By Extension</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>2</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Interfaccia utente</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ordina per estensione</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this action is turned on, the main sorting key in the &krusader; panel "
"becomes the file extension (the part of the filename after the last '.'). "
"This is useful for grouping files of the same type closer together."
msgstr ""
"Quando questa azione è attivata, la chiave principale di ordinamento, "
"all'interno del pannello di &krusader;, è l'estensione del file (la parte "
"del nome del file dopo l'ultimo punto). Questa opzione è utile al fine di "
"mantenere vicino tutti i file dello stesso tipo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>3</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>User Interface</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Sort By Size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>3</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Interfaccia utente</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ordina per dimensione</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this action is turned on, the main sorting key in the &krusader; panel "
"becomes the file size. This is useful for determining the largest files in a "
"particular folder."
msgstr ""
"Quando questa azione è attivata, la chiave principale di ordinamento, "
"all'interno del pannello di &krusader;, è la dimensione del file. Questa "
"opzione è utile per determinare i file più grandi all'interno di una "
"specifica cartella."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>4</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Useractions</guimenu><guisubmenu>User Interface</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Sort By Modified</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Meta; <keycap>4</keycap> </keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Azioni</guimenu><guisubmenu>Interfaccia utente</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ordina per modificato</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this action is turned on, the main sorting key in the &krusader; panel "
"becomes the last modified date for each file. This is useful for finding "
"files you recently worked on."
msgstr ""
"Quando questa azione è attivata, la chiave principale di ordinamento, "
"all'interno del pannello di &krusader;, è l'ultima data di modifica per "
"ciascun file. Questa opzione è utile per individuare i file cui hai lavorato "
"di recente."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tools Menu"
msgstr "Menu Strumenti"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Cerca...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens <link linkend=\"krusearcher\">KruSearcher</link> - the &krusader; "
"search module."
msgstr ""
"Apre <link linkend=\"krusearcher\">KruSearcher</link>, il modulo di ricerca "
"di &krusader;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locate...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Localizza..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"locate\">Locate</link> &GUI; frontend for fast "
"file searching."
msgstr ""
"Apre l'interfaccia <link linkend=\"locate\">Localizza</link> per la ricerca "
"rapida dei file."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Synchronize Folders</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>Y</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sincronizza cartelle</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Synchronize Folders</link> function "
"compares the left and right panels and shows the differences between them. "
"After the compare function, you can move files/folders so that they can be "
"synchronized."
msgstr ""
"La funzione <link linkend=\"synchronizer\">Sincronizza cartelle</link> "
"confronta i pannelli destro e sinistro e ne mostra le differenze. Dopo aver "
"eseguito la funzione, puoi spostare i file e le cartelle, affinché possano "
"essere sincronizzate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>/</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>MountMan...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt; <keycap>/</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>MountMan...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens submenu with items to open <link linkend=\"mount-man\">MountMan</link> "
"or mount/unmount various mounting points."
msgstr ""
"Apre il sotto-menu con elementi per aprire <link linkend=\"mount-man"
"\">MountMan</link> o montare/smontare vari punti di montaggio."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Disk Usage...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>S</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uso del "
"disco...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens <link linkend=\"diskusage\">Disk Usage</link>."
msgstr "Apre la finestra <link linkend=\"diskusage\">Uso del disco</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Net Connection</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nuova connessione di "
"rete</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">New Network Connection</link> "
"dialog to start a &FTP;, SMB, FISH or SFTP connection to a remote host. If "
"you leave the user name and password fields empty, you will login as "
"anonymous. You can <link linkend=\"bookman\">Bookmark</link> these remote "
"sessions."
msgstr ""
"Apre la finestra <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">Nuova connessione di "
"rete</link> in cui avviare una connessione &FTP;, SMB, FISH o SFTP verso un "
"host remoto. Se lasci vuoti i campi nome utente e password, accederai come "
"anonimo. Puoi inserire queste sessioni remote tra i <link linkend=\"bookman"
"\">Preferiti</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Disconnect From "
"Net</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>D</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Disconnetti "
"dalla rete</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Ends the <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">remote connection</link> in "
"the active panel and returns to the start-up path."
msgstr ""
"Termina la <link linkend=\"remote-connections\">connessione remota</link> "
"nel pannello attivo e restituisce il percorso iniziale."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start Terminal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Avvia terminale</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a terminal window in the default folder (usually your home folder). "
"You can choose your favorite terminal application in the <link linkend="
"\"konfig-general\">Konfigurator General page</link>."
msgstr ""
"Apre una finestra di terminale nella cartella predefinita (in genere la tua "
"cartella home). Puoi scegliere la tua applicazione di terminale preferita "
"nella <link linkend=\"konfig-general\">pagina Generale di Konfigurator</"
"link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>K</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Start Root Mode "
"Krusader</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>K</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Avvia "
"Krusader in modalità amministrazione</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Starts &krusader; in <link linkend=\"root-mode\">Root mode</link> at the "
"same location. Root mode &krusader; requires <command>kdesu</command> by "
"default, if <command>kdesu</command> is not available or if you prefer &eg; "
"<command>gksu</command> when using <ulink url=\"https://www.gnome.org"
"\"><application>GNOME</application></ulink> you can change this behaviour in "
"the <link linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">Konfigurator Dependencies page</"
"link>."
msgstr ""
"Avvia &krusader; in <link linkend=\"root-mode\">modalità amministrazione</"
"link> nell'attuale posizione. La modalità amministrazione di &krusader; "
"richiede per impostazione predefinita <command>kdesu</command>, se "
"<command>kdesu</command> non è disponibile o se preferisci, per esempio, "
"<command>gksu</command> se usi <ulink url=\"https://www.gnome.org"
"\"><application>GNOME</application></ulink> puoi cambiare questo "
"comportamento nella <link linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">pagina Dipendenze "
"di Konfigurator</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Be careful when using &krusader; with ROOT PRIVILEGES."
msgstr ""
"Presta attenzione quando usi &krusader; con PRIVILEGI DI AMMINISTRAZIONE."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Empty Trash</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Strumenti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Svuota il cestino</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Empties the <link linkend=\"deleting\">trash bin</link>."
msgstr "Svuota il <link linkend=\"deleting\">cestino</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: menu-commands.docbook:1346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Window Menu"
msgstr "Menu Finestra"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Tab</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nuova scheda</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1361
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens a new tab in the active panel."
msgstr "Apre una nuova scheda nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lock Tab/Unlock Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Blocca scheda/Sblocca scheda</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locks then unlocks current tab in the active panel."
msgstr "Blocca e sblocca la scheda attiva nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Duplicate Current Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>N</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Duplica scheda attiva</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a new tab that is a duplicate of the active tab in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"Apre una nuova scheda che è il duplicato della scheda attiva nel pannello "
"attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Move Current "
"Tab to Other Side</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>O</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sposta la "
"scheda attiva nell'altro lato</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moves current tab to the other side of &krusader; window."
msgstr "Sposta la scheda attiva nell'altro lato della finestra di &krusader;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Current Tab</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>W</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Chiude la scheda attiva</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Closes the current tab in the active panel. This command is only available "
"if there is more than one tab in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"Chiude la scheda attiva nel pannello attivo. Questo comando è disponibile "
"solo se è presente più di una scheda nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Inactive Tabs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Chiude la scheda inattiva</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes all the tabs in the active panel except for the active."
msgstr ""
"Chiude tutte le schede nel pannello attivo, ad eccezione di quella attiva."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Duplicated Tabs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Chiudi schede duplicate</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the duplicated tabs in the active panel."
msgstr "Chiude le schede duplicate nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nuova scheda</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigates to the next tab in the active panel. This command is only "
"available if there is more than one tab in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"Passa alla scheda successiva nel pannello attivo. Questo comando è "
"disponibile solo se è presente più di una scheda nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Tab</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Scheda precedente</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigates to the previous tab in the active panel. This command is only "
"available if there is more than one tab in the active panel."
msgstr ""
"Passa alla scheda precedente nel pannello attivo. Questo comando è "
"disponibile solo se è presente più di una scheda nel pannello attivo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Profiles</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift; <keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Profili</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1493
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a menu where <link linkend=\"panel_profiles\">Panel profiles</link> "
"can be saved and restored."
msgstr ""
"Apre un menu in cui i <link linkend=\"panel_profiles\">profili dei pannelli</"
"link> possono essere salvati e ripristinati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Swap Panels</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Scambia pannelli</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The left panel will become the right panel and vice versa, only the current "
"tabs will be swapped."
msgstr ""
"Il pannello sinistro diventa il destro e viceversa, solo le schede attive "
"vengono scambiate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1516
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Swap Sides</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Shift; <keycap>U</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Scambia lati</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The complete left panel will become the right panel and vice versa, and all "
"tabs will be swapped."
msgstr ""
"Tutto il pannello sinistro diventa il destro e viceversa, e tutte le schede "
"vengono scambiate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt; <keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vertical Mode</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"> &Ctrl;&Alt; <keycap>R</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Modo "
"verticale</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles the <link linkend=\"list_panel\">List Panel</link> between "
"horizontal and vertical mode."
msgstr ""
"Alterna il <link linkend=\"list_panel\">pannello degli elenchi</link> tra il "
"modo orizzontale e quello verticale."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt; <keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Toggle "
"Fullscreen Terminal Emulator</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt; <keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Commuta "
"visualizzazione a tutto schermo del terminale</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggles full screen mode of the terminal emulator. This option is only "
"available when <guilabel>Show Terminal Emulator</guilabel> is activated."
msgstr ""
"Alterna la modalità a tutto schermo del terminale. Questa opzione è "
"disponibile solo se l'opzione <guilabel>Mostra emulatore di terminale</"
"guilabel> è attivata."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: menu-commands.docbook:1568
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Window</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Position</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Finestra</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Salva posizione</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: menu-commands.docbook:1574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saves the current size and position of the &krusader; main window. This "
"action can be automated with <guilabel>Save last position, size and panel "
"settings</guilabel> in <link linkend=\"konfigurator\">Konfigurator Startup "
"page</link>"
msgstr ""
"Salva la posizione e la dimensione correnti della finestra principale di "
"&krusader;. Questa opzione può essere resa automatica con l'opzione "
"<guilabel>Salva ultima posizione, dimensione e impostazioni dei pannelli</"
"guilabel> nella <link linkend=\"konfigurator\">pagina Avvio del "
"Konfigurator</link>."

